
On Ubuntu 18.04 LTS -
    1. Wireshark - For packet capture
    2. PCRE - Perl Compatible Regular Expression
    3. Libnet - Network Functions
    4. DAQ - Data AcQuisition Modes
    
i) sudo apt-get install -y build-essential (reference for all packages needed to compile a Debian
package)
ii) sudo apt-get install -y libpcap-dev libpcre3-dev libdumbnet-dev
iii) mkdir ~/snort_src
iv) cd ~/snort_src

